#compdef kdialog
# Documentation: https://develop.kde.org/docs/administration/kdialog/
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: KDE kdialog upstream — dialog boxes for shell scripts.
# Real flag set: --yesno, --yesnocancel, --warningyesno,
# --warningcontinuecancel, --warningyesnocancel, --sorry,
# --detailedsorry, --error, --detailederror, --msgbox, --inputbox,
# --password, --newpassword, --combobox, --menu, --checklist,
# --radiolist, --passivepopup, --getopenfilename, --getsavefilename,
# --getexistingdirectory, --getopenurl, --getsaveurl, --textbox,
# --textinputbox, --progressbar, --getcolor, --title, --default,
# --multiple, --separate-output, --print-winid, --dontagain,
# --icon, --ok-label/--cancel-label/--yes-label/--no-label/
# --continue-label, --attach, --embed, --geometry.
